sub_title: CEO at Wiztopic, Empowers communication teams with a software to manage their daily challenges
summary:
Wiztopic is the publisher of a new software platform for communication executives.

In just under two years, its enterprise cloud based solution has become a standard for listed companies (Schneider Electric, Capgemini, Nexity, Faurecia) and the banking/insurance sector (BPCE, Crédit Agricole, AG2R, Allianz, Covéa, Humanis, KPMG).
